Localization.Name: DMC
Localization.Description: Still renowned for their denim, DMC (Denim Manufacture Corporation) has become so much more. From durable outerwear to rugged fashion, DMC knows that feeling good is just as important as looking good.

Localization.Name: ASD Bomber Jacket
Localization.Description: Carrying Capacity: 2K µSCU\n\nAssociated Science and Development is a company that defines what it means to be on the bleeding edge of technology. Originally exclusive to ASD workers in the Biological Research Division, this synthetic leather has the look, feel, and smell of the real thing. The company's logo is featured on the front and back.
